title: Statistics and Accounts of Cultural Enterprises (EMPCULT). 2013 [+] (IDESCAT - Statistical Institute of Catalonia) ...
text: ( Source : IDESCAT - Statistical Institute of Catalonia ) The turnover carried out by cultural enterprises in Catalonia amounted to 9,684 billion euros in 2013, its added gross value rose to 3,470 billion euros and it employed 103,963 people.
